&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &#x27;Verdana&#x27;,sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: &#x27;Times New Roman&#x27;; mso-bidi-font-family: &#x27;Times New Roman&#x27;; mso-fareast-language: EN-CA;&quot;&gt;For more information and additional drop-off locations visit &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.productcare.org/products/hhw/ontario/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: blue;&quot;&gt;productcare.org/products/hhw/ontario/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
