&lt;li&gt;Alternatively, place in a clear plastic bag or in an open cardboard box and set on the ground on Garbage collection day 0.5 metre (2 feet) away from your Garbage Bin. Residents of apartments/condos should take electronics to their building&amp;rsquo;s designated drop-off area.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
