&lt;ul&gt; 
 &lt;li&gt;Empty and rinse (if necessary and possible) this item, then place metal end in can and pinch closed before placing in your &lt;strong&gt;Blue Bin&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt; 
 &lt;li&gt;Place plastic pull-off strips in your &lt;strong&gt;Garbage Bin&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt; 
